	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It might be going into "junk mail" filters that pick up on spammers who imitate the standard phpBB confirmation message. Rewrite the text of the confirmation message in your own words, and it will more easily pass through content-based filters.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


